text: Khairpur District () is a district in the Sindh province of Pakistan. The district has an area of 15,910 square kilometres and is headquartered at the city of Khairpur. ==Administration== The district has eight Talukas (counties): * Khairpur * Nara Tehsil * Kot Diji Tehsil * Sobho Dero Tehsil * Mirwah Tehsil * Kingri Tehsil * Faiz Ganj Tehsil * Gambat Tehsil Category:Khairpur District
title: Khairpur District
